            "title": "龍旗科技暗盤高開 中段較招股價高近20%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍旗科技(09611)將於明天掛牌，今年暗盤價高開逾3%，其後升勢擴大，截至下午約5時26分的暗盤價較招股價高近20%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"龍旗科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Longcheer-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"龍旗科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Longcheer-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">龍旗科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股以上限每股31元定價，按輝立交易平台資料，龍旗科技暗盤暫報36.64元，高於招股價逾18%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤價37.08元，較招股價高19.61%。</p>\n</div>",
